Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.generaltree

Class GeneralTreeNode

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.tree.generaltree.GeneralTreeNode
public class GeneralTreeNode extends Object

Title: GeneralTreeNode

Description:

Helper class to establish the nodes in a binary tree. Given that a node can have zero or more children we can make use of a vector or array to store the number of children for a given node.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
